## @file
#  MP driver installs MP protocol.
#
#  MP Dxe is a fork of CpuDxe that focusing only on the non-BSP AP initialization. This is required for Patina as
#  Patina will implement the CPU initialization for the BSP, including interrupts, GDT, MTRR, and paging. This driver
#  is intended to be use in place of CpuDxe for platforms that require the gEfiMpServiceProtocolGuid protocol. For
#  history of the copied code, see the CpuDxe implementation.
#
#  Reference: https://github.com/tianocore/edk2/tree/master/UefiCpuPkg/CpuDxe
